500
00:25:07,525 --> 00:25:12,630
the notion of competitive gaming as incredible content

501
00:25:12,630 --> 00:25:16,274
and an incredible experience for gamers is here to stay.

502
00:25:16,274 --> 00:25:18,115
And I think in five to 10 years,

503
00:25:18,115 --> 00:25:22,700
we're gonna see a much wider variety of formats,

