506
00:25:29,787 --> 00:25:33,773
If you're building a game or an e-sport or experimenting in

507
00:25:33,773 --> 00:25:37,418
e-sports, I want to encourage you to choose a model for your

508
00:25:37,418 --> 00:25:38,200
e-sport.

509
00:25:38,200 --> 00:25:38,780
