510
00:25:40,796 --> 00:25:43,057
blindly look at what's going on in another game

511
00:25:43,057 --> 00:25:44,037
and sort of copy paste it.

512
00:25:44,037 --> 00:25:46,518
If you're a game developer, try to spend

513
00:25:46,518 --> 00:25:49,559
the same kind of effort in crafting your eSport

514
00:25:49,559 --> 00:25:50,899
that you spend in crafting your game.

515
00:25:50,899 --> 00:25:53,380
And when you do that,

516
00:25:53,380 --> 00:25:56,221
think about what you want your players to value,

517
00:25:56,221 --> 00:25:57,641
both from the competition

518
00:25:57,641 --> 00:25:59,362
and how they should think about competition,

519
00:25:59,362 --> 00:26:01,842
and what you want their players to value from each other.

